title: Joon Maeng Pre-Season 2013 Interview @ Spyder Auto
description: Spyder Auto's Robert Theys takes a few moments to talk with Formula Drift driver Joon Maeng to talk about the Lucas Oil/Road Race Engineering 240SX hatch with V8 power he'll be running for the 2013 Formula Drift season. We're just days ahead of the Formula Drift season opener on the Streets of Long Beach.
